Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.38,SPEC3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(450,308)\be10\fad(0,250)}企劃3「怪物恐慌」\N應徵<来制作游戏吧>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白是不是在以自己的方式想了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千尋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是不能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己很拚命的時候  看到鬆懈了的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是誰都會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師您是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要去揭學生的傷疤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是因為明白才不想被揭傷疤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白她並沒有鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是不知道該如何面對前所未有的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對不知道該怎麼和好的真白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再以這種不清不楚的感情去對待她怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是讓我去道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  你真是個小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是白就是黑的這種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上的事才沒有那麼簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎所有的事都是那麼曖昧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是黑色或是白色  而是灰色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過如果一味地只追求自己心中最理想狀態的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己和周圍的人都會陷入不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白的事你給我解決了  以上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為我是真白的負責人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年年末  櫻花莊就要封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去澳大利亞玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你回老家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣  太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣  那一天到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知該如何是好的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是否該傳遞出去的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定暫時不表達出去的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交錯  交織  碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而後擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那蛋糕就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是晚上五點之後再來取
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要忘記哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼福  眼福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣   學弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛到你都說不出話來了啊  是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像你很習慣穿這類衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頒獎典禮的時候也要穿禮服的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  穿上大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  仁學長  就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用跑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也會參加櫻花莊的派對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦  還要交換聖誕禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得要準備哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真讓人頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對不知道該怎麼和好的真白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再以這種不清不楚的感情去對待她怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太  剛才那封信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是應徵的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會再看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下就由我先借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  九點半再在這裏見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大衣就先給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地和我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名  要好好和別人打招呼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地和我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊  你到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青…山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用那麼吃驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有些意外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感覺氛圍有點不一樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這樣的青山也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  挺驚訝的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就很成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土豪現充什麼的都給我爆炸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要給我擅自掛掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我和龍之介說話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你個鄉下佬竟然寄來了這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還恬不知恥的打來電話沒有常識也該有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢話少說  快把龍之介交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  下得好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會積起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪的話淋到也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來拿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要用我的傘的話  這點事總歸要做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戲劇你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是嚇了一跳 也感覺有點不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對演員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我在玩遊戲的時候也會想一樣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,專業人士果然從發聲到演技都完全不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加油了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話不該對正在努力的人說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有在加油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山當然在努力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少感覺得出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩月份有個試鏡這將決定是不是能所屬於事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後家裏人說如果進不了事務所的話就回大阪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是字面的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果試鏡失敗的話  就轉校回大阪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果進入事務所的話就一邊工作一邊讀水高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不在了的話  你會覺得寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山會成功的  絕對會成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  還有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試鏡要是通過了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:16:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候  希望你能聽我說件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候再說  現在不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了的話就會僵掉的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我會聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有啊  要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是到那時我還扭扭捏捏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛向宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要管是什麼啦  對我說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道是怎麼回事  不過我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君  我是綾乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名在你那嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  椎名她不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽酒店的人說  她出酒店了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她會去什麼地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山  拿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我  認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡你  我喜歡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真的一直都很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪  停了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞋子怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走著走著就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃  所以想給空太吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才跑出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…空太最近一直在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…有很多話想和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你卻一直一副厭惡的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在想該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼樣才能讓空太開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼才能讓你高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…卻想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…能做的只有這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然一聲不吭就不見了會讓我很擔心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然不見了  哪裏都找不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你是不是遇上交通事故了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心臟都嚇得要停了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我有些自覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光著腳跑到這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還弄傷手指
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是專業的漫畫家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太的事  我有認真考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…就想試試看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前都沒有想過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本從來沒有過這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到你畫漫畫的時候  真的很震撼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有衝擊力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不去思考妥協之後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拚命地去畫著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像是理所當然的一樣賭上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那之後我的視線就已經離不開真白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那個時候開始我就喜歡上了這樣的真白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要讓我失望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我注視著你  有好好地注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆打算這樣站著到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你到底從什麼時候開始在那的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴你的話神田君估計連死的心都會有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不要告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很重要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能再陪我做發表的練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要  我也要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  漆黑一片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…在忙於夜晚的活動？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事可不能直接說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我要進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到極限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門沒鎖…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我努力過了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為了成為他的戀人努力過了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我無法珍惜你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使那樣也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:22:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.01,0:23:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白仁在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就保持這個樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.79,0:23:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持著這個我喜歡的美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  不是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天  我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要被仁傷害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.58,0:23:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然帶著三個姑娘光榮返鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兒子果然是受一點刺激馬上就能成長起來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觸頗深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
